Flea Market Tallahassee
Calendar of Events
When we say we have something for everyone, we mean it. Jeeptoberfest every October, The Military Vehicle Show every February, Antique Engine and Tractor Show twice a year, The Gourd Show, the Back to Basic’s Expo, Antique Car shows, Motorcycle Rally’s, Stamp Camp (for those that make cards), RC Races, and numerous bake sales and fund raisers for local schools and organizations.
